---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service" description="Blackout Pickleball terms of service for purchases and site usage.">

  <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-surface">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-lg">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-black tracking-tight mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-text-light"><em>Last updated: May 2026</em></p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Orders & Payment</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">
        All purchases are processed securely through Stripe. By placing an order, you agree to pay the listed price plus any applicable shipping. Prices are in USD.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Shipping</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">
        Orders are shipped within the United States. Shipping times and costs are calculated at checkout. We aim to ship all orders within 3–5 business days.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Returns & Exchanges</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">
        We want you to love your Blackout gear. If something doesn't fit right or arrives damaged, contact us within 14 days of delivery at <a href="mailto:info@brandblackout.com" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-dark">info@brandblackout.com</a> and we'll work it out.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">
        All content, designs, and branding on this site are property of Blackout Pickleball. Unauthorized reproduction is prohibited.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">
        Questions about these terms? Email us at <a href="mailto:info@brandblackout.com" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-dark">info@brandblackout.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
